         !text "               Gunslinger               "
         !text "           (c) 1986 DataSoft            "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "programming . . . . . . . . .Allen Adham"
         !text "graphics. . . . . . . . . Evan Ballinger"
         !text "thanks. . . . . . . . . . .Bill Mitchell"
         !text "  . . . . . . . . . . . . . Andy Thorsen"
         !text "  . . . . . . . . . . . .Hedrick 6-South"
         !text "                                        "
         !text "You are Kip Starr, former Texas Ranger. "
         !text "You've been peacefully traveling the    "
         !text "west since your lawman days, but your   "
         !text "past has finally caught up with you!    "
         !text "Your old Ranger pal, James Badland, a   "
         !text "hotheaded young fellow, is in trouble.  "
         !text "He's in jail in Tijuana and due for     "
         !text "hanging in two days. On top of that, the"
         !text "Dalton brothers, all six of them, are   "
         !text "out of jail and gunning for you.        "
         !text "                                        "
         !text "Find adventure in a gold-rush ghost     "
         !text "town, an Indian village, and a US Army  "
         !text "fort on your way to Mexico to rescue    "
         !text "James from the hangman's noose.         "
         !fill $40
